    "description_full": "The strategy is a long only, cross sectional momentum system designed to harvest short term trend persistence in a curated basket of high retail participation U.S. equities and thematic proxies (meme stocks, high beta tech, crypto related equities, ARKK and similar). The core signal is the sign change of a smoothed price curvature estimate: it seeks names with positive price velocity and positive inferred near term trend, and exits immediately when the estimated price acceleration flips from positive to negative, aiming to avoid holding through momentum regime breaks and downside convexity common in speculative names.\n\n",
